<title type="html"><![CDATA[3/20 (Sun.) Taiwan’s I-Mei Foods plans environmental campaign to mark 88th anniversary/My journey to thank...(Host: Mei)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=600&amp;p=623#p623"><![CDATA[
3/20 (Sun.) Taiwan’s I-Mei Foods plans environmental campaign to mark 88th anniversary / My journey to thank all the people responsible for my morning coffee (Host: Mei)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:35 pm Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:35-9:00 pm Debate<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br />----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />Article #1: Taiwan’s I-Mei Foods plans environmental campaign to mark 88th anniversary <br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/4457155">https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/4457155</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1.What kind of I- Mei food have you bought mostly or/ and are so impressed by? And why?<br /><br />2.What do you think the reason is for I-Mei food company to be selected seven years in a row as Taiwan’s most valuable consumer brand by Kantar Group survey?<br /><br /><br />3.We are happy to see I-Mei will launch a series of promotional activities related to the protection of the environment. Except for some of the events will take place for special date, do you have any recommendations for things food companies can do to protect our environment more efficiently?<br /><br />4.In Taiwan, there are many traditional food companies that have operated for over 30 years or so, and have good reputation and a lot of regular consumers. Please introduce some of the food stores you know to us. <br /><br />---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br /><br />Article #2 : My journey to thank all the people responsible for my morning coffee<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L375-rWJVmU&amp;list=RDCMUCAuUUnT6oDeKwE6v1NGQxug&amp;index=1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L375-rW ... ug&amp;index=1</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1. According to the speaker, one of the best weapons to fight the brain's negative bias like anxiety, anger and depression is gratitude. do you believe that claim or do you have any other recommendations?<br /><br />2. What item or a thing do you need to have every day? Without it you will feel anxious or you might not live well.<br /><br />3. Can you try to write down the number of people and things that are related to the item which you answered in question 3? If it’s possible, how do you express your gratefulness?<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=46353">Ellen Lu</a> — Tue Mar 15, 2022 2:40 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
